<ThingDefs><List>

	<ThingDef Type="Item" Name="Mod_trib_fabao_forbiddenseal" Parent="MiBaoBase">
		<ThingName>Forbidden Seal</ThingName>
		<TexPath>res\Sprs\object_zhengfatianxia\object_PTfu01</TexPath>
		<FabaoTexPath>res\Sprs\object_zhengfatianxia\object_MBfu01</FabaoTexPath>
		<Desc>A primordial artifact forged by an immortal who waged war against the Heavenly Dao. The forbidden hex inscribed upon this talisman draws power directly from Heaven's Condemnation, converting divine punishment into overwhelming Spell prowess. At full power, this seal can silence the heavens themselves.</Desc>
		<ElementKind>None</ElementKind>
		<Item Kind="Equipment">
			<PhysicalLables>
				<li>Light2</li>
				<li>Soft1</li>
			</PhysicalLables>
			<BeMade>
				<WorkToMake>1</WorkToMake>
				<CostItems>
					<Item name="Item_Wood" count="1"/>
				</CostItems>
			</BeMade>
			<Fabao>
				<ActiveCondition>
					<Condition eventid="Other" des="Have 1 Condemnation or more." needcount="1"/>
				</ActiveCondition>
				<SpecialAbility>
					<Ability Kind="Sync_AddEquptDataModifier" sParam1="Mod_trib_modifiers_fabao1" Desc="Each point of Condemnation will improve the user Spell prowess."/>
				</SpecialAbility>
			</Fabao>
			<UseLua>GameMain:GetMod('_FabaoHelper'):FabaoActivePenalty()</UseLua>
		</Item>
		<Element>
			<Kind>None</Kind>
		</Element>
		<ProduceMode>
			<WorldDrop>1</WorldDrop>
			<DropRate>5</DropRate>
		</ProduceMode>
	</ThingDef>
	<ThingDef Type="Item" Name="Mod_trib_item_heavenrendingsword" Parent="MiBaoBase">
		<ThingName>Heaven-Rending Sword</ThingName>
		<TexPath>res\Sprs\object_zhengfatianxia\object_PTfu01</TexPath>
		<FabaoTexPath>res\Sprs\object_zhengfatianxia\object_MBfu01</FabaoTexPath>
		<Desc>A primordial divine sword forged from the bones of the first heaven. It hungered for ten thousand years before finding a worthy wielder. One swing can rend the heavens, split the earth, and annihilate an entire sect. No defense can withstand it. No life can endure its edge.</Desc>
		<ElementKind>Jin</ElementKind>
		<Item Kind="Equipment">
			<PhysicalLables>
				<li>Heavy2</li>
				<li>Hard2</li>
			</PhysicalLables>
			<BeMade>
				<WorkToMake>1</WorkToMake>
				<CostItems>
					<Item name="Item_Wood" count="1"/>
				</CostItems>
			</BeMade>
			<Fabao>
				<ActiveCondition>
					<Condition eventid="Other" des="Passive — always active." needcount="0"/>
				</ActiveCondition>
				<SpecialAbility>
					<Ability Kind="Sync_AddEquptDataModifier" sParam1="Mod_trib_modifiers_fabao_heavenrendingsword" Desc="Heaven-Rending Sword: absolute combat supremacy in all areas."/>
				</SpecialAbility>
			</Fabao>
		</Item>
		<Element>
			<Kind>Jin</Kind>
		</Element>
		<ProduceMode>
			<WorldDrop>1</WorldDrop>
			<DropRate>3</DropRate>
		</ProduceMode>
	</ThingDef>

	<ThingDef Type="Item" Name="Mod_trib_item_sectdestroyer" Parent="MiBaoBase">
		<ThingName>Sect-Destroyer Talisman</ThingName>
		<TexPath>res\Sprs\object_zhengfatianxia\object_PTfu01</TexPath>
		<FabaoTexPath>res\Sprs\object_zhengfatianxia\object_MBfu01</FabaoTexPath>
		<Desc>An ancient talisman inscribed with the war-edicts of a sovereign who toppled seven hundred sects in a single day. The hatred of ten thousand fallen cultivators is compressed within it, thirsting for more destruction. When activated, all enemy defenses crumble and all allied attacks become absolute.</Desc>
		<ElementKind>None</ElementKind>
		<Item Kind="Equipment">
			<PhysicalLables>
				<li>Light2</li>
				<li>Soft1</li>
			</PhysicalLables>
			<BeMade>
				<WorkToMake>1</WorkToMake>
				<CostItems>
					<Item name="Item_Wood" count="1"/>
				</CostItems>
			</BeMade>
			<Fabao>
				<ActiveCondition>
					<Condition eventid="Other" des="Passive — always active." needcount="0"/>
				</ActiveCondition>
				<SpecialAbility>
					<Ability Kind="Sync_AddEquptDataModifier" sParam1="Mod_trib_modifiers_fabao_sectdestroyer" Desc="Sect-Destroyer Talisman: omnipotent sect-razing power."/>
				</SpecialAbility>
			</Fabao>
		</Item>
		<Element>
			<Kind>None</Kind>
		</Element>
		<ProduceMode>
			<WorldDrop>1</WorldDrop>
			<DropRate>3</DropRate>
		</ProduceMode>
	</ThingDef>

</List></ThingDefs>
